title: Where's Nexus Siege?
body: Please tell me it's not disabled :(

replies.body:
It's not disabled, it's just that the rotating queue doesn't start until 11am (AEST).

So that's 2 more hours until you can play!
Ohh silly me, thanks haha :O any idea where I could find this time to reference next time?
[Here you go](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/BX05N9lh-queue-schedule-updated-for-615).  **Riot Gehirn** usually keeps that post pretty updated with any new changes.
